==Spanish==

===Phrase===
'''[[te#Spanish|te]] [[quiero]]'''

# [[I love you]].

Implies affection, love, care, not necessarily lustful.You can say te quiero to your mother, father , sibling, etc.  It is similar to "Te Amo" (which actually means I love you), Te Amo is usually reserved for one's lover.

